{"title":"Post #3 Collection features a small handlebar, top tube & saddle bag with unique features","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/10/26/post-3-collection-features-a-small-handlebar-top-tube-saddle-bag-with-unique-features/","date":1635274527000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142757/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-green.jpg\" data-fancybox=\"\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142757/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-green-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142757/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-green-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142757/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-green-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142757/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-green-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142757/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-green-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142757/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-green.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></a><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-276354\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>There are already a&nbsp;<em>lot&nbsp;</em>of bags out there. Yet, some brands are still finding ways to innovate—which seems to be the case for Post Carry Co. While the company’s Founder &amp; Lead Designer, Marc Mendoza, acknowledges the sea of options, Marc thinks that the #3 collection will stand out.</p><h2>Mini Handlebar Bag</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142808/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-red.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142808/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-red.jpg\" alt=\"Post #3 Collection handlebar bag\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142808/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-red.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142808/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-red-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142808/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-red-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142808/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-red-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142808/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-red-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142920/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-red-jules.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142920/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-red-jules.jpg\" alt=\"Post #3 Collection handlebar bag\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142920/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-red-jules.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142920/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-red-jules-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142920/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-red-jules-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142920/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-red-jules-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142920/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-red-jules-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>For those looking to stash some items upfront, the Mini Handlebar bag could be a great option for shorter rides. The bag has an internal plastic reinforcement that will keep its shape, and a three-point connection to keep it from sagging. The opening is uniquely positioned so that it allows access even if your bar is loaded up with electronics. And a 180-degree zipper helps cram stuff inside.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142751/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-blue-back-studio.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142751/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-blue-back-studio.jpg\" alt=\"Post #3 Collection handlebar bag mini\" width=\"1200\" height=\"834\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142751/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-blue-back-studio.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142751/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-blue-back-studio-297x206.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142751/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-blue-back-studio-800x556.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142751/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-blue-back-studio-120x83.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142751/post-carry-co-mini-handlebar-bag-blue-back-studio-768x534.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>Measuring 20 x 10 x 10cm, the bag is constructed from 600D outer and 200D inner polyester fabric with a #3 Ykk zipper. For those that want to use it, there is a stabilizing drawstring on the back for the head tube or steerer, but it can also be removed. Offered in six colors, some bags have reflective accents. Weighing in at 125g, the bags are priced at $40.</p><h2>The Bomber Top Tube Bag</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142831/post-carry-co-the-bomber-frame-bag-top-tube-comparison.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142831/post-carry-co-the-bomber-frame-bag-top-tube-comparison.jpg\" alt=\"Post #3 Collection the bomber top tube bag\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142831/post-carry-co-the-bomber-frame-bag-top-tube-comparison.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142831/post-carry-co-the-bomber-frame-bag-top-tube-comparison-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142831/post-carry-co-the-bomber-frame-bag-top-tube-comparison-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142831/post-carry-co-the-bomber-frame-bag-top-tube-comparison-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142831/post-carry-co-the-bomber-frame-bag-top-tube-comparison-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>The Bomber is probably the most unique offering with a flip-flop design that can be used beneath&nbsp;<em>or</em> on top of the top tube.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142835/post-carry-co-the-bomber-gray-studio.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142835/post-carry-co-the-bomber-gray-studio.jpg\" alt=\"Post #3 Collection the bomber top tube bag\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142835/post-carry-co-the-bomber-gray-studio.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142835/post-carry-co-the-bomber-gray-studio-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142835/post-carry-co-the-bomber-gray-studio-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142835/post-carry-co-the-bomber-gray-studio-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142835/post-carry-co-the-bomber-gray-studio-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>That includes a bolt-on option for top-tube use which will allow you to ditch the front strap. Also, the size #3 YKK zipper is on the side of the bag which allows access in either position.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142839/post-carry-co-the-bomber-lay-flat.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142839/post-carry-co-the-bomber-lay-flat.jpg\" alt=\"Post #3 Collection the bomber storage\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142839/post-carry-co-the-bomber-lay-flat.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142839/post-carry-co-the-bomber-lay-flat-297x297.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142839/post-carry-co-the-bomber-lay-flat-800x800.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142839/post-carry-co-the-bomber-lay-flat-120x120.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142839/post-carry-co-the-bomber-lay-flat-768x768.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142839/post-carry-co-the-bomber-lay-flat-125x125.jpg 125w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>In spite of the thin profile, the bag will still fit a pump up to 35cm in length and has dimensions of 38 x 6 x 4cm. Like the Mini Handlebar Bag, the Bomber uses a PE plastic reinforced construction with 600/200D polyester fabric.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142843/post-carry-co-the-bomber-straps.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142843/post-carry-co-the-bomber-straps.jpg\" alt=\"Post #3 Collection the bomber strap\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142843/post-carry-co-the-bomber-straps.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142843/post-carry-co-the-bomber-straps-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142843/post-carry-co-the-bomber-straps-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142843/post-carry-co-the-bomber-straps-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142843/post-carry-co-the-bomber-straps-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>The Bomber includes different strap lengths to fit different sized frame tubes and comes in three colors for $35.</p><h2>Saddle Bag</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142823/post-carry-co-saddle-bag-black-open-studio-e1635273931569.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142823/post-carry-co-saddle-bag-black-open-studio-e1635273931569.jpg\" alt=\"Post #3 Collection seat post bag\" width=\"834\" height=\"531\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142823/post-carry-co-saddle-bag-black-open-studio-e1635273931569.jpg 834w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142823/post-carry-co-saddle-bag-black-open-studio-e1635273931569-297x189.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142823/post-carry-co-saddle-bag-black-open-studio-e1635273931569-800x509.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142823/post-carry-co-saddle-bag-black-open-studio-e1635273931569-120x76.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142823/post-carry-co-saddle-bag-black-open-studio-e1635273931569-768x489.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 834px) 100vw, 834px\"></a></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142817/post-carry-co-saddle-bag-black-on-plants-flash.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142817/post-carry-co-saddle-bag-black-on-plants-flash.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142817/post-carry-co-saddle-bag-black-on-plants-flash.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142817/post-carry-co-saddle-bag-black-on-plants-flash-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142817/post-carry-co-saddle-bag-black-on-plants-flash-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142817/post-carry-co-saddle-bag-black-on-plants-flash-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26142817/post-carry-co-saddle-bag-black-on-plants-flash-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>Finally, the Saddle Bag is a minimalist design that only weighs 56g. Again, a plastic reinforced design helps keep the bag’s shape, and a #3 YKK zipper offers 180° access. Measuring 13 x 6 x 5cm, the bag is meant to fit one spare lightweight tube and tools to fix a flat, and sells for $30.</p><p><a href=\"https://postcarry.co/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>postcarry.co</em></a></p></section></article></div></div>","author":"Zach Overholt","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"2e07df3b95e3c51239ada4e173965e3abfbc9dc6dde3fa6310d3a151021b5e26","category":"Cycling"}